OL,3,CGordon Brown asks Met for new probe
OL,4,Cinto phone hacking amid 'cover up'
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FGordon Brown tells ITV News Political
OL,8,FEditor Robert Peston why he's called
OL,9,Ffor a fresh probe over phone hacking
OL,10,Fby Rupert Murdoch's News International
OL,12,FFormer Prime Minister Gordon Brown has
OL,13,Fwritten to the head of the Met Police
OL,14,Fto call for a new criminal
OL,15,Finvestigation into News International
OL,16,Fover phone hacking.
OL,18,FA decade ago the police conducted an
OL,19,Finvestigation into hacking. Its boss
OL,20,FRebekah Brooks was prosecuted and
OL,21,Fcleared.
