OL,3,CGordon Brown asks Met for new probe
OL,4,Cinto phone hacking amid 'cover up'
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FBut today Brown is calling for a new
OL,8,Fpolice probe after new information in
OL,9,Fcourt documents allege a massive cover-
OL,10,Fup by News International, which reveal
OL,11,Fthat he was accused of being in a
OL,12,Fconspiracy to obtain internal emails.
OL,14,FThis supposed security threat to the
OL,15,Fowner of the News of the World and The
OL,16,FSun was allegedly used to explain to
OL,17,Fpolice why millions of emails - that
OL,18,Fmay have been key evidence - were
OL,19,Fdestroyed.
