OL,3,CGordon Brown asks Met for new probe
OL,4,Cinto phone hacking amid 'cover up'
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FNews Group Newspapers said Brown's
OL,8,Fallegations are "unfounded and wrong",
OL,9,Fthat they relate to events that are a
OL,10,Fdecade old but are the subject of
OL,11,Fcurrent proceedings in civil courts.
OL,13,FBrown told ITV News Political Editor
OL,14,FRobert Peston it was "astonishing" to
OL,15,Fdiscover the allegations against him.
