OL,3,CGordon Brown asks Met for new probe
OL,4,Cinto phone hacking amid 'cover up'
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,F"We've known for some time that the
OL,8,Fnews group destroyed about 30 million
OL,9,Femails," he says. "But what we didn't
OL,10,Fknow was the explanation that they
OL,11,Fwere giving to the police for why
OL,12,Fthey'd done this.
OL,14,F"And it is totally shocking to think
OL,15,Fthat what they should do is allege
OL,16,Fthat I and Tom Watson should have been
OL,17,Fbribing one of their employees... to
OL,18,Ftry to get hold of their emails.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/15
