OL,3,CGordon Brown asks Met for new probe
OL,4,Cinto phone hacking amid 'cover up'
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,F"And their pretext for destruction was
OL,8,Fthat I was engaged in trying to get
OL,9,Fthis information... and of course,
OL,10,Fit's not true."
OL,12,FBrown has today written to the
OL,13,Fcommissioner of the Metropolitan
OL,14,FPolice, Sir Mark Rowley, saying the
OL,15,Ftheft and bribery accusations are
OL,16,F"completely untrue" and requesting a
OL,17,Fmeeting as a precursor to a new
OL,18,F"criminal investigation".
