OL,3,CGordon Brown asks Met for new probe
OL,4,Cinto phone hacking amid 'cover up'
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FWhat has incensed Brown is statements
OL,8,Fin recent court documents that on
OL,9,FJanuary 22 2011, News International IT
OL,10,FExecutive Paul Cheesbrough emailed
OL,11,FBrooks and the general manager, Will
OL,12,FLewis, saying Brown had a sympathiser
OL,13,Finside News International who was
OL,14,Fstealing Brooks's emails.
OL,16,FOn February 11, Cheesbrough asked for
OL,17,Fan investigation of the potential
OL,18,Ftheft of data that was allegedly being
OL,19,Fpassed to Labour MP, Tom Watson, who
OL,20,Fwas close to Brown.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/15
