OL,3,CGordon Brown asks Met for new probe
OL,4,Cinto phone hacking amid 'cover up'
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FAnd then on July 8, months after the
OL,8,FMet Police had been investigating
OL,9,Fphone hacking, Cheesebrough and Lewis
OL,10,Ftold the police there had been a
OL,11,Fsuspected theft of Brooks's emails,
OL,12,Fthat Watson had been handling this
OL,13,Fstolen data, and that he was working
OL,14,Fin a conspiracy with Brown.
OL,16,FThis, they told the police, was why
OL,17,Fmillions of emails had been deleted,
OL,18,Faccording to minutes of that meeting
OL,19,Freferenced in publicly available case
OL,20,Fdocuments.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/15
