OL,7,F"That's a matter that I continue to
OL,8,Fconsider," Brown says. "But the
OL,9,Fimportant thing for me is not what
OL,10,Fhappened to me. Now, the important
OL,11,Fthing for me is that people have got a
OL,12,Fright to privacy."
