OL,3,CGordon Brown asks Met for new probe
OL,4,Cinto phone hacking amid 'cover up'
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,F"You've got to look at what happened
OL,8,Fin 2005 as a result of the bombings in
OL,9,FLondon - the terrorist incident - and
OL,10,Fwhat happened to members of these
OL,11,Ffamilies. You've also got to look at
OL,12,Fthe Madeleine McCann case.
OL,14,F"Was News International and were the
OL,15,Fjournalists and were the private
OL,16,Finvestigators involved in invading the
OL,17,Fprivacy of people at the moment of
OL,18,Ftheir greatest grief, at the moment
OL,19,Fwhen they were most vulnerable?"
